                "description": "<p>A map of attribute values as they appear before or after the <code>UpdateItem</code> operation, as determined by the <code>ReturnValues</code> parameter.</p> <p>The <code>Attributes</code> map is only present if <code>ReturnValues</code> was specified as something other than <code>NONE</code> in the request. Each element represents one attribute.</p>"
